We'll use the vault.

01:04:30.033 --> 01:04:32.241
Divide it evenly among these ten accounts.

01:04:34.954 --> 01:04:37.492
No problem.
Pleasure to have your business.

01:04:37.582 --> 01:04:39.039
Looking forward to have much more.

01:04:41.461 --> 01:04:42.747
Yes.

01:04:45.965 --> 01:04:48.799
You're supposed to eat your food,
not wear it.

01:04:49.886 --> 01:04:51.530
You worked late,
