What do they all have in common?

01:11:02.091 --> 01:11:04.424
Bought with loans
by the same bank in Liechtenstein.

01:11:04.510 --> 01:11:05.510
Same forms, even.

01:11:05.512 --> 01:11:08.595
Liechtenstein. Jesus.
The secrecy laws there.

01:11:08.681 --> 01:11:09.717
Hit the lights.

