comes from here.

01:11:17.356 --> 01:11:20.190
And this man is singing like a canary.

01:11:20.610 --> 01:11:22.170
And has the bank records to back it up.

01:11:23.112 --> 01:11:26.321
- Now, where's the trail start?
- It starts here.

01:11:26.407 --> 01:11:29.445
Deposit in the Cayman Islands
to a whole host of companies.

01:11:29.535 --> 01:11:32.323
But it's dope cash rolling in
every day by the wheelbarrow.

01:11:32.705 --> 01:11:34.537
Half a billion dollars last year alone.

01:11:34.624 --> 01:11:35.785
All cash.

01:11:35.875 --> 01:11:37.366
Here's how we think it lays out.

01:11:38.169 --> 01:11:40.661
From our investigation, a large network.

01:11:41.631 --> 01:11:44.499
Nice family. Who's the guy on top?

01:11:45.134 --> 01:11:47.467
That right there, that's Robbie Reemer.

01:11:51.557 --> 01:11:54.550
What is this?
