01:12:04.987 --> 01:12:06.944
Forget the royals and the celebs.

01:12:07.031 --> 01:12:08.863
We just got us some government money!

01:12:09.242 --> 01:12:14.112
Sincerely, William Van Raab,
Commissioner, U.S. Coast Guard.

01:12:14.205 --> 01:12:17.949
Ten million dollars!
Couldn't get any richer!

01:12:18.793 --> 01:12:20.705
Well, break out the fuckin' champagne!

01:12:20.795 --> 01:12:23.879
- Come on, buddy!
- We did it!

01:12:23.965 --> 01:12:25.172
- Yeah.
